    "long_instructions": "## Video Game Developer - Level 3: Multi-Shot Prompting\r\n\r\nPractice multi-shot prompting through the career of a video game developer by guiding the AI with clear structure and multiple expectations for the dialogue.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a prompt like the one below, or write a similar one that breaks the task into parts and gives specific goals for the conversation.\r\n\r\n>Create a dialogue where a hero confronts a villain in an abandoned city. First, describe the villain’s motivation, then build tension with a heated argument, and end with the hero preparing to stop the villain’s plan.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the added structure affects the story flow, character depth, and tension.",
